<span id="Description"></span>
== Описание ==

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
The '''TechDraw CommandAddOffsetVertex''' tool adds a cosmetic vertex at a specified offset from a selected vertex.
</div>

[[Image:TechDraw_CommandAddOffsetVertex_Example.png|200px]]
<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
{{Caption|Selected vertex and added cosmetic vertex}}
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
==Usage==
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
# Select a vertex.
# There are several ways to invoke the tool:
#* Press the {{Button|[[Image:TechDraw_CommandAddOffsetVertex.svg|16px]] [[TechDraw_CommandAddOffsetVertex|Add an offset vertex]]}} button.
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|TechDraw → Extensions: Centerlines/Threading → [[Image:TechDraw_CommandAddOffsetVertex.svg|16px]] Add an offset vertex}} option from the menu.
# A task panel opens.
# Enter the desired (positive or negative) {{MenuCommand|X-Offset}} and {{MenuCommand|Y-Offset}} in mm.
# Press the {{Button|OK}} button.
# A cosmetic vertex is added.
</div>


